snippet.title: Garden of the Sea - Official Nintendo Switch Trailer | Wholesome Direct 2024
snippet.description:
Explore the colorful world of Garden Of The Sea in this trailer for the upcoming adventure game. The trailer showcases how you can grow your garden, decorate your home, some of the creatures you'll meet, and areas you can explore. Garden Of The Sea will be available on Nintendo Switch and Steam. 

In Garden Of The Sea, you wake up on a small island in a magical world. Grow your garden, nurture local creatures, furnish your home or adventure across the seas to explore more islands and gather new resources. This world is for you.
